      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they will shoot you right then and then on the spot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to hit you.",
      "word_count": 5
